Cristiano Ronaldo's uncertain future at Manchester United continues to dominate the headlines with the Portuguese international set to miss a second successive day of training ahead of Friday's pre-season tour of the Far East and Australia. Yet there is more positive news emerging from Old Trafford in regards to incomings as Erik ten Hag looks to up the ante in pursuit of new signings. Express Sport brings you the latest done deals and rumours from the transfer market on Tuesday, July 5...